	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've never seen a Famicom cart do anything with the Famicom audio.
<br />It would probably cost too much to do anything with the Famicom audio, besides using a cap to roll off the highs.
<br />Most carts I've seen just mix it using 2 resistors.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
